divs: Sighting DetailsDriving in my Neighborhood i approached a stop sign facing the western sky, it was Approx. 9:20PM, I saw Two Large Triangular objects Silently and very slowly hovering. one was going south bound and the other western, judging by the speed i was driving the object seemed to be traveling at a steady pace with me at 30 mph. I snapped a photo on my cell phone when i approached the stop sign of the vehicle heading south.
Summary: 2 Large Silent Slow Triangular objects Hover Through Sky Approx. 200Ft. High
